Package me.wobblyyyy.edt

Interface ItrTrio<A,​B,​C>

  • Type Parameters:
    A - the first of three arguments.
    B - the second of three arguments.
    C - the third of three arguments.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TrioIterator
    public interface ItrTrio<A,​B,​C>
    An iteration trio for sets that have three consumed arguments.
